com.ckeiner.testbddy.core.reporting

Interface ReportElement

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExtentElement

    public interface ReportElement
    Depicts an element, that is created by the ReportInterface. This way, each BDD component can be logged depending on whether it failed or was skipped among others.
    Author:
    ckeiner
